  "title": "Animated Pufferfish Totem",
  "description": "A small addon for Refined Buckets and Punchy that makes the Totem of Undying appear as an animated pufferfish bucket when held.",
  "body": "<p>\n  Makes the <strong>Totem of Undying</strong> appear as an <strong>animated pufferfish bucket when held</strong>, powered by Punchy and Refined Buckets.\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0b566fb8def522cb658008a9a49539e9c16678c3_0.webp\"\n       width=\"420\"\n       alt=\"Pufferfish bucket replacing the Totem of Undying when held\">\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/lqNBiv3L/images/5d2f2d918a9f0193a9c74b6eaa07606227392e95.gif\"\n       width=\"420\"\n       alt=\"Animation demo showing the Totem transforming into an animated pufferfish bucket when held\">\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\"><em>Animation demo: vanilla totem in inventory, animated pufferfish bucket when held</em></p>\n\n<h3 align=\"center\">🔗 Requirements</h3>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/refined-buckets\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5f76489844cb9eca9c773e370b5c982ad3ef05fa.png\"\n         width=\"300\"\n         alt=\"Requires Refined Buckets resource pack\">\n  </a><br><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/punchy-fpa\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/fad1074568a3441a24b311f5b453c45bb9e2b619.png\"\n         width=\"270\"\n         alt=\"Requires Punchy mod\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n### ⚙️ Installation\n\n1. Install **Refined Buckets** and **Punchy**\n2. Place this resource pack **above Refined Buckets**\n\n**Troubleshooting**\n- If the held item looks misaligned or behaves strangely, try disabling *Item Physics* in Punchy settings\n\n### 📜 Credits\n\n- Refined Buckets for models and animations  \n- Punchy for the item animation system  ",
